    <title>Ubuntu18.04 配置备忘</title>
    <link href="https://blog.solarzhcl.com/2018/07/31/Ubuntu18-04-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98/"/>
    <id>https://blog.solarzhcl.com/2018/07/31/Ubuntu18-04-配置备忘/</id>
    <published>2018-07-31T13:09:45.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-07-31T13:24:10.842Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>记录目前ubuntu中安装的应用和相关配置<br><a id="more"></a></p><hr><h1 id="主题："><a href="#主题：" class="headerlink" title="主题："></a>主题：</h1><ul><li>网站：<ul><li>snwh.org: <a href="https://snwh.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://snwh.org/</a></li><li>gnome-look: <a href="https://www.gnome-look.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.gnome-look.org</a></li></ul></li><li>应用程序:安装至<code>/usr/share/themes/</code> 或 <code>~/.local/share/themes/</code><ul><li><a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1215199/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Telinkrin-Buttons-left</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1220749/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Canta theme</a></li></ul></li><li><p>图标：安装至<code>/usr/share/icons/</code> 或 <code>~/.local/share/icons/</code></p><ul><li><a href="https://snwh.org/paper" target="_blank" rel="noopener">paper</a></li><li><a href="https://snwh.org/suru" target="_blank" rel="noopener">suru</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1166289/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">papirus</a> : manjaro默认图标</li><li><a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1148695/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">La-Capitaine</a></li></ul></li><li><p>光标：安装至<code>/usr/share/icons/</code> 或 <code>~/.local/share/icons/</code></p><ul><li><a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1148692/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Capitaine-cursors</a></li></ul></li><li>字体：<ul><li>Monaco</li></ul></li></ul><h1 id="应用"><a href="#应用" class="headerlink" title="应用"></a>应用</h1><h2 id="需要下载"><a href="#需要下载" class="headerlink" title="需要下载"></a>需要下载</h2><ul><li><a href="http://community.wps.cn/download/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WPS</a></li><li><a href="https://gitee.com/wszqkzqk/deepin-wine-for-ubuntu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">deepin-wine</a></li><li><a href="https://www.lulinux.com/archives/1319" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TIM / QQ</a></li><li><a href="http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">deepin容器</a></li><li><a href="https://www.lulinux.com/archives/1319" target="_blank" rel="noopener">微信</a></li><li><a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">vscode</a> 编辑器</li><li><a href="http://www.getmailspring.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">mailspring</a> 现代风格的邮件客户端</li><li><a href="http://www.jetbrains.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">jetbrains</a> 官网</li><li><a href="http://app.leanote.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Leanote</a>   云笔记</li><li><a href="http://staruml.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">StarUML</a> UML</li></ul><h2 id="直接安装"><a href="#直接安装" class="headerlink" title="直接安装"></a>直接安装</h2><ul><li>remmina<blockquote><p>sudo apt install remmina</p></blockquote></li><li><p>Quiterss：rss订阅</p><blockquote><p>sudo apt install quiterss</p></blockquote></li><li><p>Shadowsocks-qt5</p><blockquote><p>sudo add-apt-repository ppa:hzwhuang/ss-qt5<br>sudo apt-get update<br>#修改<code>/etc/apt/sources.list.d/hzwhuang-ubuntu-ss-qt5-bionic.list</code>文件,将 bionic 改成 xenial<br>sudo apt-get install shadowsocks-qt5</p></blockquote></li><li><p>Bleachbit：清理工具</p><blockquote><p>sudo apt-get install bleachbit</p></blockquote></li><li><p>chrome</p><blockquote><p>sudo wget <a href="http://www.linuxidc.com/files/repo/google-chrome.list" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://www.linuxidc.com/files/repo/google-chrome.list</a> -P /etc/apt/sources.list.d/<br>wget -q -O - <a href="https://dl.google.com/linux/linux_signing_key.pub" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://dl.google.com/linux/linux_signing_key.pub</a>  | sudo apt-key add -<br>sudo apt-get update<br>sudo apt-get install google-chrome-stable</p></blockquote></li><li><p>redshift：调整屏幕色调</p><blockquote><p>sudo apt-get install redshift redshift-gtk</p></blockquote></li><li><p>openshot 视频编辑</p><blockquote><p>sudo apt install openshot</p></blockquote></li><li><p>GIMP 图片编辑</p><blockquote><p>sudo apt install gimp</p></blockquote></li><li><p>kdenlive 视频编辑</p><blockquote><p>sudo apt install kdenlive</p></blockquote></li><li><p>calibre 图书管理</p><blockquote><p>sudo apt install calibre  </p></blockquote></li><li><p>zeal API查看</p><blockquote><p>sudo apt install zeal</p></blockquote></li><li><p>translate-shell 命令行翻译工具</p><blockquote><p>sudo apt install translate-shell</p><p># 配合 xsel和通知 实现划词桌面划词翻译</p><p># 编写脚本文件，加入开机自启</p></blockquote>  <figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#!/usr/bin/env bash</span></span><br><span class="line">se=$(xsel -o)</span><br><span class="line">re=$(/usr/bin/trans -b en:zh <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$se</span>"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">notify-send <span class="string">"\$se"</span> <span class="string">"\$re"</span> -i accessories-dictionary -t 2000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="gnome-shell"><a href="#gnome-shell" class="headerlink" title="gnome-shell"></a>gnome-shell</h2><ul><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">gnome shell extensions</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/750/openweather/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">openweather</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/941/show-ip/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">show ip</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/826/suspend-button/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">suspend button</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/779/clipboard-indicator/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Clipboard Manager</a> 剪切板管理</li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/690/easyscreencast/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">EasyScreenCast</a> 屏幕录制</li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/841/freon/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">freon</a> 主板cpu温度显示</li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/1263/gnomehub/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gnomehub</a> 快速访问github 源</li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/1190/ip-finder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ip finder</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/36/lock-keys/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">lock keys</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/55/media-player-indicator/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Media player indicator</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/1267/no-title-bar/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">No title bar</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/118/no-topleft-hot-corner/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">No hot corner</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/1254/obmin/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Obmin</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/708/panel-osd/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Panel OSD</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/977/recent-items/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">recent items</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/800/remove-dropdown-arrows/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">remove dropdown arrows</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/1085/simple-net-speed/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">simple net speed</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/1031/topicons/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">topicon plus</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/131/touchpad-indicator/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">touchpad indicator</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/48/trash/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">trash</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/1112/screenshot-tool/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">screenshot tool</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/120/system-monitor/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">system-monitor</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/19/user-themes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">user themes</a></li><li><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/7/removable-drive-menu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Removable Drive Menu</a></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;记录目前ubuntu中安装的应用和相关配置&lt;br&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
